athways to\napproach molecular systems in Chemistry: electronic structure, molecular\ndynamics and statistical mechanics. This is done with the aid of some\nillustrative examples -- theoretical developments in some cases and numerical\nsimulations in other cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 13:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-16"}
